quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Zvirokwazvo, makare-kare takava tinopa Ibrahim (Abrahamu) nhungamiro yake (kunzira yakatwasuka), uye taiziva nezvake (kutenda kwake)"
  21,52,"Apo paakataura kuna baba vake nevanhu vake kuti: “Zviumbwa izvi, zviyi izvo munoperera pakuzvinamata?”"
  21,53,"(Vanhu vake) vakataura kuti: “(Izvi) takawana zvichinamatwa namadzitateguru edu.”"
  21,54,"(Abrahamu) akataura kuti: “Zvirokwazvo, imi nemadzibaba enyu makarasika zviri pachena.”"
  21,55,"(Vanhu) vakapindura vachiti: “Wauya nechokwadi here kwatiri kana kuti uri kuita zvekutamba?”"
  21,56,"(Abrahamu) akataura kuti: “(Zivai kuti) Tenzi venyu ndiTenzi (mumwechete Allah) vedenga nenyika, avo vakazvisika, uye ini kwazviri (pakusikwa kwazvo naAllah) ndinopa uchapupu.”"
  21,57,"“Uye ndinopika naAllah, zvirokwazvo ndichatsvaga zano rekuputsa zvidhori zvenyu mushure mekunge imi mambofamba-famba.”"
  21,58,"Nokudaro, akazviputsa kuita zvidimbu-zvidimbu, zvese kusara kwechihombe pakati pazvo, kuitira kuti vachibvunze (aputsa zvidhori)"
  21,59,"(Vanhu vadzoka) vakataura kuti: “Ndiani aita izvi kunanamwari vedu? Zvirokwazvo, mutadzi mukuru.”"
  21,60,"(Vamwe) vanhu vakati: “Takanzwa kamwe kamukomana kanonzi Abrahamu kachingotaura nezvazvo (zvidhori kuti kachazviputsa).”"
  21,61,"(Vamwe) vakati: “Huyai naye pamberi pevanhu kuti vave vanomuona (vave neuchapupu nezvake (Abrahamu)).”"
  21,62,"(Vanhu) vakati: “Ndiwe here waita izvi kuvanamwari vedu, iwe Abrahamu?”"
  21,63,"(Abrahamu) akati: “Asi ichi chihombe chazvo (zvidhori) ndicho chaita izvi. Zvibvunzei kana zvichigona kutaura!”"
  21,64,"Saka vakataura pachavo kuti: “Zvirokwazvo, muri vatadzi vakuru.”"
  21,65,"Uye vakazova vanopindura (pfungwa yavo) vakati: “Zvirokwazvo, iwe (Abrahamu) unoziva kuti (zvidhori) hazvitauri!”"
  21,66,"(Abrahamu) akati: “Saka munonamatirei izvo zvisingakubatsirei, kana kukukuvadzai muchisiya Allah?”"
  21,67,"“Mashoko akaipa kwamuri, imi neizvo zvamunonamata muchisiya Allah! Hamupfungi here?”"
  21,68,"(Vanhu) vakati: “Mupisei (Abrahamu) mubatsire vanamwari venyu, hunge muchizviita (muchizvikwanisa).”"
  21,69,"Takataura (Allah) kuti: “Iwe Moto! Iva unotonhora wopa ruchengetedzo kuna Abrahamu!”"
  21,70,"Uye vaida kumukuvadza, asi takavaita vanhu vakarasikirwa zvikuru"
  21,71,Uye takamuponesa iye naLoti (Lut) kunyika yakakomborerwa kuvanhu nezvinhu zvose
  21,72,Uye takamupa (vana) Ishaaq (Isaka) uye (muzukuru) Ya’qoob (Jakobho). Vose takavaita vana vakatwasuka
  21,73,"Uye takavaita vatungamiriri vaitungamira vanhu nokuda kwedu, uye tikavakomekedza kuita mabasa akanaka, kuita Swalaah (Minamato), uye kupa Zakaah (kupa Swadaqah kwevapfumi kuvarombo mushure kwegore), uye vainamata Isu (Allah) chete"
  21,74,"Uye Loti takamupa ungwaru neruzivo, uye tikamuponesa kubva muguta iro raiitwa zvakashata. Zvirokwazvo, vaiva vanhu vakashata vaiita zvivi"
  21,75,"Uye takamupinza mutsitsi dzedu. Zvirokwazvo, aiita mabasa akanaka"
  21,76,Uye (rangarirai) apo Nowa akachema kwatiri makare. Takamupindura uye tikamuponesa iye nemhuri yake kubva kumarwadzo makuru
  21,77,"Takamubatsira kubva kune vanhu avo vairamba mashoko edu. Zvirokwazvo, vaiva vanhu vaiita mabasa akashata. Saka vese takavanyudza"
  21,78,"Uye (rangarirai) Dawood (Dhavhidha) naSulaimaan (Soromoni) pavaitonga maererano nebindu iro rakanga radyiwa namakwai avanhu usiku, uye takanzwa kutonga kwavo"
  21,79,"Uye takaita kuti Sulaimaan (Soromoni) anzwisise (nyaya yacho), uye vose takavapa hungwaru neruzivo. Uye takaita kuti makomo neshiri zvitirumbidze pamwechete naDhavhidha. Uye ndisu takazviita (zvese)"
  21,80,"Uye takamudzidzisa kugadzira nguwo dzehondo dzesimbi, kuti dzikudzivirirei mukurwa kwenyu. Muchava munotenda here"
  21,81,Uye Soromoni takaita kuti mhepo ive inovhuvhuta zvakasimba nekuda kwake ichienda kunzvimbo iyo yatakakomborera. Uye tinoziva zvese
  21,82,"Uyezve kune mamwe maJinn (zvisikwa zvakasikwa nemoto) ayo haimunyurira (Soromoni mumvura achitsvaga matombo akakosha nezvimwe zvinhu), uye zvakare achiita rimwe basa rakasiyana neirori, uye takanga tirisu taivachengetedza"